# Common Issues

## "Domain is invalid or disabled by admin"

This usually occurs shortly after registering a new `.co.zw` domain.

Wait for the registry to complete domain activation.

---

## WHOIS shows no DNS records

This is common while a newly registered domain is propagating.

Wait several hours before troubleshooting.

---

## Invalid CNAME

Incorrect

```
www → 16.192.59.194
```

Correct

```
A @ → 16.192.59.194

CNAME www → blessed.co.zw
```

---

## Invalid MX

Incorrect

```
MX → 16.192.59.194
```

Correct

```
mail A → 16.192.59.194

MX → mail.blessed.co.zw
```

---

## Mail Record Proxied

Always configure the `mail` A record as **DNS Only**.

