---

# Best Practices

- Proxy only website traffic.
- Keep mail-related records as DNS Only.
- Configure SPF, DKIM, and DMARC.
- Configure reverse DNS with your VPS provider.
- Use HTTPS for your website.
- Test DNS before troubleshooting applications.

